<p><b>  Algeria</b>*<b>, China</b>*<b>, Cuba</b>*<b>, Ecuador, Egypt</b>*<b>, Ethiopia, India, Pakistan, Russian 
Federation</b>*<b>, Saudi Arabia</b>*<b>, South Africa</b>*<b>, United Arab Emirates, Venezuela 
